  "body": "1. This component shall contain:\r\n\r\n- `model` property where the expected model is a `ListModel` type and each `ListElement` contains `emoji`, `name` and `selected` properties.\r\n- A `next` button to slide through the tags.\r\n- The tags row width shall be dynamically adjusted and the position of the `next` button shall be modified according to that. If width is big enough, the `next` button shall be hidden.\r\n- tags entries shall be `clickable` and `selectable`. Once the selected property is changed, emit a signal.\r\n- `emoji size` shall be configurable, so expose a property accordingly.\r\n- `text size` should be configurable, so expose a property accordingly.\r\n- Review position /spacing of emoji and text in base component `StatusListItemTag`.\r\n- Tags will have proper hover indicators.\r\n\r\n2. It will look like (related figma file [here](https://www.figma.com/file/17fc13UBFvInrLgNUKJJg5/Kuba%E2%8E%9CDesktop?node-id=2090%3A245814)):\r\n\r\n![Screenshot 2022-05-25 at 08 22 05](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/97019400/170194020-9731386f-fac2-4e2c-a4d4-505979917455.png)\r\n\r\n![Screenshot 2022-05-25 at 08 22 29](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/97019400/170194082-2afba5a8-c32b-4377-bad5-1e2f67833d3a.png)\r\n\r\n3. A frist implementation can be found in (once this component is created, replace existing code in both files):\r\n\r\n- desktop --> _../app/AppLayouts/CommunitiesPortal/CommunitiesPortalLayout.qml_\r\n\r\n- StatusQ --> _../Components/StatusCommunityCard.qml_\r\n\r\n4. Add an example in `sandbox` project.",
